{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/nesting-for-loops","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Ugnjezdene for Petlje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako imate visedimenzionalni niz, mozete primeniti istu logiku kao ranije da prolazite kroz niz i sve njegove podnizove. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const arr = [\n  [1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]\n];\n\nfor (let i = 0; i &#x3C; arr.length; i++) {\n  for (let j = 0; j &#x3C; arr[i].length; j++) {\n    console.log(arr[i][j]);\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo ispisuje svaki pod-element iz <code>arr</code> redom. Obratite paznju da u unutrasnjoj petlji proveravamo <code>.length</code> od <code>arr[i]</code>, jer je <code>arr[i]</code> sam niz.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244e1","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite funkciju <code>multiplyAll</code> tako da vraca proizvod svih brojeva u podnizovima <code>arr</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18248,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/nesting-for-loops"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function multiplyAll(arr) {\n  let product = 1;\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return product;\n}\n\nmultiplyAll([[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6, 7]]);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>multiplyAll([[1], [2], [3]])</code> treba da vrati <code>6</code></p>","testString":"assert(mul